>>>To Find about how parameter sets are designed for powershell cmdlet

http://blog.simonw.se/powershell-functions-and-parameter-sets/
================================================================================================================================

>>>To update the help files
   Run Update-Help

>>>To find information about some command let for eg need to know what cmdlet/function available about process:
   Run  Get-Help *process*

>>>Once you select particular cmdlet to dig further we can use
   Run  Get-Help Get-Process /  Get-Help Get-Process -Full

>>>To Know about particular parameter like ComputerName we can use
   Run  Get-Help Get-Process -parameter ComputerName
   
>>>To list all the possible parameter sets for Get-Process run
   Run   Get-Command -Name Get-Process -Syntax
